videos.description: Colorado's early 3-point shooting helps to spark the Buffalo's offense.
videos.headline: Coloardo's 3-point barrage surges offense

videos.description: Oregon's Jordan Bell gets the great pass from Dillon Brooks, but Bell is denied by the rim on his dunk attempt. Colorado's Wesley Gordon is called with the foul.
videos.headline: Bell gets denied by the rim and draws the foul

videos.description: Oregon's Jordan Bell gets the block and Tyler Dorsey takes it down court and gets the lucky roll on his lay-in.
videos.headline: Oregon turns a block into two points

videos.description: After a failed alley-oop attempt, Colorado's Derrick White hits back-to-back 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Colorado responds to miss with two 3-pointers.

videos.description: Colorado's Josh Fortune grabs the rebound off a missed Oregon 3-pointer as the Buffalo's Xavier Johnson finishes with a finger roll.
videos.headline: Colorado capitalizes off missed 3-pointer

videos.description: Colorado's Derrick White hits a 3-pointer to help pad the Buffalo's lead over Oregon.
videos.headline: Colorado's White nails a key 3-pointer

videos.description: Colorado fans storm the court as the Buffaloes upset the No. 10 ranked Oregon Ducks.
videos.headline: Colorado fans storm court in celebration of win over Oregon
